Mura Quick Site Builder
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INTRODUCTION
Quick Site Builder is a simple Mura CMS Utility plugin that allows you to quickly create 
Categories and Pages. Select the top-level category you want to populate and place each 
item on its own line in the provided textarea. 
Sub-pages and sub-categories are denoted by a hyphen in front.  


Sample Category Structure:

Category
-Sub Cat 1
-Sub Cat 2
Category 2
-Sub Cat 3
-Sub Cat 4
--Sub Sub Cat 1
Category 3

Sample Page Structure:

Products
-Product 1
Services
Support
About
-Jobs
Contact

